<h2 class="page-header">Team Formation Rules</h2>
<ul>
<li>Girls and boys to form mixed teams.</li>
<li>Team composition: 5(on field)+2(substitutes)</li>
<li>Team should comprise of players from minimum of 3 different batches.</li>
<li>The entire college is divided into 3 pools: ‘A’ , ‘B’ , ‘C’.</li>
<li>If the team consists of two players from pool A, there must be a girl member in the team from pool C.</li>
<li>If there is only one pool A player in the team, then one girl from pool B can also be a part of the team.</li>
<li>If there are no pool A players in the team, then there is no restriction on the number of pool B and pool C players in the team.</li>
<li>M-tech, Phd, MSc and Faculty will be considered different batches.</li>
<li>If there are more than three PG or faculty in a team, the batch constraint will be relaxed to 2 different batches.</li>
</ul>
